{{doc/start}}
Renders a styled infobox for a Sky Platform (Space Station) upgrade. Data is pulled automatically from [[Module:Data/SkyPlatformUpgrades]]. The infobox displays the upgrade's name, category, power requirement, item costs, prerequisite upgrades, required research, and effects (power increase, build speed, sector unlocks, trade licenses, hangar space).

Pages using this template are auto-generated by <code>foundry_parser generate-pages</code>. Editors can add content below the infobox but should not modify the template call itself.

== Data source ==
Sky Platform upgrade data comes from [[Module:Data/SkyPlatformUpgrades]], which is auto-generated by running:
<pre>foundry_parser generate-lua</pre>
from the game installation at <code>F:\SteamLibrary\SteamApps\common\FOUNDRY</code>. Do not edit data modules directly.

== Usage ==
<pre>
{{Infobox Sky Platform Upgrade|id=_base_spu_power_i}}
{{Infobox Sky Platform Upgrade|id=_base_spu_power_i|image=Power Upgrade I.png}}
</pre>

== Parameters ==
{| class="wikitable"
! Parameter !! Description !! Type !! Status
|-
| <code>id</code> || Sky Platform upgrade template identifier from the game data (e.g. <code>_base_spu_power_i</code>). || String || Required
|-
| <code>image</code> || Image filename to display. The module prepends <code>Item_</code> automatically. Sky Platform upgrade images are typically stored as <code>File:Item_NAME (Space Station).png</code>. || String || Optional
|}

== Notes ==
* The category label is derived from <code>category_id</code> by stripping the <code>_base_</code> prefix and title-casing; <code>Rd</code> is corrected to <code>R&D</code>.
* Endless upgrades (repeatable) are additionally categorised into <code>[[Category:Endless Upgrades]]</code>.
* The infobox automatically adds <code>[[Category:Sky Platform Upgrades]]</code>.
{{doc/end}}
